Homework #2

Create beginning portion of a security program for the business, describing the purpose of this document.

Who is responsible for overall creation/enforcement of it?

Where does it originate from (what body? CEO, Board, etc.)?

How does it support the business?

What is the governance for the security program document?

Create an initial policy page with list of desired policies (This is only a list. It will grow. Do not write any policies yet).
